// Minimap
// Collapsible line-overview minimap for the document editor's scrollable
// content. Renders a thumbnail-scale version of the markdown content and
// provides a drag handle to scroll the main editor.

FUNCTION Minimap(content, scrollPosition, onScrollTo, isVisible) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a scaled-down preview of the document (via transform:scale).
  A viewport indicator rectangle overlays the visible portion.
  Dragging the indicator or clicking the minimap calls onScrollTo with the
  target scroll percentage.
  Hidden when isVisible is false (parent can toggle via toolbar).
